int C[100],N,K;

void back(int k){
	
	int i;
	if (k==K+1){
		for (i=1;i<=K;++i)
			 printf("%d ", C[i]);
		printf("\n");
	}
	else
		for (i=C[k-1]+1;i<=N-K+k;++i){
				 C[k]=i;
				 back(k+1);
			 }
}
